# Diktat.ai Design System & Styling Rules

## Core Design Principles

### 1. Glass-morphism & Modern Aesthetics

- Use semi-transparent backgrounds with backdrop blur effects
- Layer multiple gradients for depth and visual interest
- Maintain consistent opacity variations for hierarchy

### 2. Brand Color System

**Primary Brand Colors:**

- **Indigo**: `indigo-500`, `indigo-600`, `indigo-700` (primary brand color)
- **Purple**: `purple-600`, `purple-700` (secondary brand color)
- **Brand Gradient**: `bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-600` (signature brand gradient)

**Secondary Colors:**

- **Emerald/Green**: Success states, positive actions
- **Amber/Orange**: Warnings, premium features
- **Red/Rose**: Errors, deletions
- **Blue**: Information, secondary actions
- **Gray**: Text hierarchy, backgrounds

### 3. Component Patterns

**Card Components:**

```css
/* Standard card pattern */
.card-pattern {
  @apply bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-sm border border-indigo-200/50 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg;
}

/* Card hover effects */
.card-hover {
  @apply hover:bg-white/80 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-200;
}
```

**Background System:**

```css
/* Primary backgrounds */
bg-white/70, bg-white/80, bg-white/90 /* Semi-transparent whites */
bg-gradient-to-br from-white/70 via-indigo-50/30 to-purple-50/30 /* Gradient backgrounds */

/* Backdrop effects */
backdrop-blur-sm, backdrop-blur-md, backdrop-blur-xl /* Glass-morphism */
```

**Border & Shadow System:**

```css
/* Borders */
border border-indigo-200/50 /* Semi-transparent borders */
border-2 border-dashed border-indigo-300/50 /* Dashed borders for upload areas */

/* Shadows */
shadow-lg, shadow-xl, shadow-2xl /* Progressive shadow depths */
shadow-indigo-100/20, shadow-indigo-500/25 /* Colored shadows */
```

### 4. Interactive Elements

**Button Hierarchy:**

```css
/* Primary buttons */
bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-600
hover:from-indigo-600 hover:to-purple-700
transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-200

/* Secondary buttons */
bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-200
hover:bg-white/90 hover:border-gray-300

/* Success/Action buttons */
bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-emerald-600
bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-indigo-600
```

**Hover States & Transitions:**

```css
/* Standard transition */
transition-all duration-200

/* Scale effects */
hover:scale-105, hover:scale-110, group-hover:scale-110

/* Shadow progression */
hover:shadow-xl, hover:shadow-2xl
```

### 5. Typography System

**Font Weights:**

- `font-bold` - Headings, important labels
- `font-semibold` - Sub-headings, emphasis
- `font-medium` - Body text, buttons

**Text Sizes:**

- `text-xs` - Small details, badges
- `text-sm` - Secondary text, descriptions
- `text-base` - Default body text
- `text-lg`, `text-xl` - Headings

**Text Colors:**

```css
/* Hierarchy */
text-gray-800 /* Primary text */
text-gray-700 /* Secondary text */
text-gray-600 /* Tertiary text */
text-gray-500 /* Subtle text */

/* Gradient text for headings */
bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent
```

### 6. Layout & Spacing

**Spacing Patterns:**

```css
/* Consistent spacing */
space-y-4, space-y-6, space-y-8 /* Vertical stacking */
gap-3, gap-4, gap-6 /* Flexbox gaps */

/* Padding system */
p-4, p-6, p-8 /* Card padding */
px-3, px-4, px-6, py-2, py-3 /* Element padding */
```

**Responsive Design:**

```css
/* Mobile-first approach */
md:block, md:hidden /* Desktop/mobile visibility */
md:pl-80 /* Sidebar offset */
lg:flex-row /* Layout changes */
```

### 7. Status & Badge Components

**Status Badges:**

```css
/* Status badge patterns */
.status-completed {
  @apply bg-green-100 text-green-800 border border-green-300;
}
.status-processing {
  @apply bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 border border-blue-300;
}
.status-failed {
  @apply bg-red-100 text-red-800 border border-red-300;
}
.status-pending {
  @apply bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 border border-gray-300;
}
```

**Icon Containers:**

```css
.icon-container {
  @apply w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center;
}
```

### 8. Premium/Pro Feature Styling

**PRO Badges:**

```css
/* Rotating PRO badge */
.pro-badge {
  @apply bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 via-orange-500 to-red-500 text-white text-xs font-bold rounded-full transform rotate-12 hover:rotate-6 transition-transform;
}

/* Glow effects */
.pro-glow {
  @apply absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 via-orange-500 to-red-500 rounded-full blur opacity-30 animate-pulse;
}
```

### 9. Animation & Loading States

**Custom Animations:**

```css
/* Pulse animation for uploads */
@keyframes pulse-upload {
  0%,
  100% {
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4);
  }
  50% {
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 15px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0);
  }
}

/* Shimmer effect for loading */
@keyframes shimmer {
  0% {
    transform: translateX(-100%);
  }
  100% {
    transform: translateX(100%);
  }
}
```

## Design Rules for New Components

### 1. Color Usage Rules

- **Primary**: Always use `indigo-500` to `purple-600` gradient for primary actions
- **Opacity**: Use `/50`, `/60`, `/70` opacity variations for layering
- **Semantic**: Maintain color semantic meaning (green=success, red=error, amber=warning)

### 2. Spacing Rules

- **Vertical spacing**: Use `space-y-4` for normal spacing, `space-y-6` for section spacing
- **Card padding**: `p-6` standard, `p-4` for smaller cards
- **Button padding**: `px-4 py-2` for normal, `px-6 py-3` for large buttons

### 3. Border & Shadow Rules

- **Borders**: Always use semi-transparent borders: `border-indigo-200/50`
- **Shadows**: Progressive shadows: `shadow-lg` â†’ `hover:shadow-xl`
- **Rounded corners**: `rounded-xl` standard, `rounded-2xl` for main cards

### 4. Interactive State Rules

- **Hover effects**: Include hover states with `hover:` prefixes
- **Transitions**: Use `transition-all duration-200` for smooth animations
- **Scale effects**: Apply `transform hover:scale-105` for button interactions

### 5. Typography Rules

- **Button text**: Use `font-medium` for buttons and important text
- **Text hierarchy**: `text-gray-700` for primary, `text-gray-600` for secondary
- **Gradient text**: Use for headings: `bg-gradient-to-r bg-clip-text text-transparent`

### 6. Glass-morphism Rules

- **Combination**: `bg-white/70` + `backdrop-blur-sm` + `border border-indigo-200/50`
- **Layering**: Layer multiple background gradients for depth
- **Hierarchy**: Use opacity variations for visual hierarchy

### 7. Component Structure Rules

- **Consistent patterns**: Follow established component patterns
- **Responsive design**: Mobile-first approach with `md:` prefixes
- **Accessibility**: Maintain proper contrast ratios and focus states

